description:
The Sabbath is a gift of rest and a day of total dependence and trust in God.

This #short clip from the message, God is Offering a Refuge of Eternal Security by Pastor Mark Finley
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kunfAgllGsM, reminds us of the significance of the Sabbath in finding shelter in God. He sanctified the Sabbath so we could experience His genuine love and care as we remember and observe it.

Watch the video to learn more about how we can find refuge through Sabbathkeeping.
